<br>
&quot; Welcome!  Please sit and warm yourself by our fire. What may I offer you to drink?&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>You watch as a small but athletic Teir'dal woman stands from a large chair near the fire.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;Allow me to introduce myself. I am Kiyda Lonjdemort.  If you have come to these halls, you must wish to join us in the destruction of all those who follow the path of light. We are a family of those who are pure evil.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Kiyda looks over your shoulder and sees a group of light bringers that consists of a dwarf, a halfling, a vah shir, a wood elf, and a high elf.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--> <br>
<br>
 &quot;Guards!  Come and get rid of this filth. Save the meat for our meal later.&quot;<br>
 <br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Suddenly, the room is filled with guards, and you watch as they are sliced up, and their blood flows on the ground.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<br>
 &quot; Excuse me, we do not tolerate filth of any kind in our halls, except to eat. Would you care for some smoked wood elf?&quot;<br>
<br>
 &quot; Come and sit down, we have much to discuss.  If you wish to join us we have a few rules that need to be followed. We seek members who have commitment to themselves (Min lvl 15), who can be trusted to rid our world of filth (we want RP), and we wish to hear your story, especially where you are and where you want to be. (we need an in-character post in the recruitment section so you can introduce yourself).&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Kiyda motions for a drink.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
