<br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>A servant brings a glass of red wine to Kiyda. She takes a drink.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
